Package: GSFirstAuthorProba
Title: Analyze Alphabetical Order in Authorship Patterns
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:person("Tom", "Broekel", email = "tobroworks@icloud.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A package to analyze authorship patterns and calculate probabilities of
    being first author based on alphabetical order in multi-author publications.
